stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> intake
    intake --> analyzing : start_analyze
    analyzing --> aligning : analyze_done (annie: JD ingest + gap analysis)
    aligning --> tailoring : align_done (echo: fresh NICE lookup, aligned OR unaligned)
    tailoring --> validating : tailor_done (synthia: STAR/ATS/NICE tailoring)
    validating --> exporting : validate_pass (vera: anti-fabrication + compliance)
    validating --> tailoring : revise (issues found, within budget)
    validating --> complete : validate_exhausted (budget spent; met=False, NO export)
    exporting --> complete : export_done (skribble: .docx to /tmp/resumes/)

    analyzing --> unknown : to_unknown
    aligning --> unknown : to_unknown
    tailoring --> unknown : to_unknown
    validating --> unknown : to_unknown
    exporting --> unknown : to_unknown
    unknown --> awaiting_clarification : escalate
    awaiting_clarification --> analyzing : clarify (re-runs pipeline; NICE lookup must be fresh anyway)

    intake --> error : abort
    analyzing --> error : abort
    aligning --> error : abort
    tailoring --> error : abort
    validating --> error : abort
    exporting --> error : abort
    unknown --> error : abort
    awaiting_clarification --> error : abort

    complete --> [*]
    error --> [*]
